title: Dark Half Discography
description:
Dark Half Discography


Members: Ian Stone & Damien Quinn 

Hometown: Wicked, WI. (K-Town) 

Genres: Horrorcore/Gore Hop/Occult Rap/Cult Shit

Label: Lyrikal Snuff Productionz/Jonestown Records




3 Albums Included:


Dark Half -2010- Chapterz

Dark Half -2012- Graveyard Bluez

Dark Half -2013- The Hemingway Solution (feat. Dope Fiend)




Bio:


Dark Half is hands downs the new wave of Wicked Shit, with there grotesque lyrics and Grunge Rock influence there an alternative approach to the Horrorcore genre!! Recently they have started a subgenre of Horrorcore that they call Cult Music a.k.a. Cult Shit, they claim to explain more about it in 2014!!
